summary: An ordinance relating to and providing for the release of the City from an undertaking to raise certain tower pole sets contained in that certain deed of perpetual easement executed by Klement and Kennedy, a co-partnership, granting a right of way over certain land in Snohomish County, Washington, to the City, for the Skagit Electric transmission system, and appropriating the sum of Twelve Hundred ($1200.00) Dollars, from the Light Fund therefor.
